com.cyc.kb.wrapper

Class ContextWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cyc.kb.wrapper.KbObjectWrapper
      • com.cyc.kb.wrapper.KbTermWrapper
        • com.cyc.kb.wrapper.KbIndividualWrapper
          • com.cyc.kb.wrapper.ContextWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Context, KbIndividual, KbObject, KbObject.KbObjectWithArity, KbTerm

    public abstract class ContextWrapper
extends KbIndividualWrapper
implements Context
    An abstract base class for implementing Contexts per the decorator pattern. To use, extend this class and implement the wrapped() method to return the wrapped object.
